  <entry>
    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Say hello to Octopress]]></title>
    <link href="http://magicwind.github.com/blog/2012/07/21/say-hello-to-octopress/"/>
    <updated>2012-07-21T16:56:00+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://magicwind.github.com/blog/2012/07/21/say-hello-to-octopress</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>First time to touch Octopress.<br/>
Very like this way to write blog.</p>

<p>为了方便记忆Octopress的各种常用命令，现制作Cheat Sheet如下：<br/>
创建新博客</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>rake new_post["title"]</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>创建新页面</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>rake new_page[super-awesome]
</span><span class='line'># creates /source/super-awesome/index.markdown
</span><span class='line'>rake new_page[super-awesome/page.html]
</span><span class='line'># creates /source/super-awesome/page.html</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>生成静态页面</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>rake generate</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>查看修改</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>rake watch</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>预览</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>rake preview</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>部署到远程服务器（之后别忘记用Git提交到github）</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>rake deploy</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>

]]></content>
